complaints room

.SH Name
.SI 5
complaints room - a place where you can file a complaint
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
complain
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a room help file.

The complaints room allows you to lodge a formal complaint about issues relating to the Disc.  

Do not take making a complaint lightly.  All complaints are considered official, and are taken very seriously.  Complaints are read by the Discworld administrative team.

Using the "complain" command, you will send an anonymous complaint which can only be seen by admin.

If you want feedback, make sure to sign the complaint with your
character's name.
.EP

.SH Commands
.SO 5 12 -22
	complain	Allows you to edit and lodge a formal complaint.
.EO

.SH Example
.SI 5
> complain
.EI

